('chunk_38cf714ed775b39f83','file_1dcbc968a2bb8c1157','visual-art.md','7. Cross-Subject Connections','- **History (Individuals & Societies):** Place the movements on a timeline — the **Renaissance** invention of linear perspective (Brunelleschi/Alberti, 1400s) and the 19th-century sequence Impressionism → Post-Impressionism → Fauvism. Link art movements to their social context (industrialisation, modern city life, new paint tubes enabling outdoor painting).
- **Mathematics:** Perspective is **geometry** — parallel lines, angles, ratios of diminishing size, and the vanishing point as a limit. Constructing accurate one/two-point grids uses the same reasoning as scale and proportion in maths.
- **Language & Literature:** **Critique writing** — using precise vocabulary, describing then analysing then evaluating an artwork, and structuring a paragraph (point → evidence → explanation) mirrors analytical essay skills. Narrative in art connects to storytelling and sequencing.
- **Science (extension):** Colour and light — how the eye perceives colour, optical mixing, and why complementary colours intensify each other links to the physics of light and human vision.','{"cross":1,"subject":1,"connections":1,"history":1,"individuals":1,"societies":1,"place":1,"the":7,"movements":2,"timeline":1,"renaissance":1,"invention":1,"linear":1,"perspective":2,"brunelleschi":1,"alberti":1,"1400s":1,"and":8,"19th":1,"century":1,"sequence":1,"impressionism":2,"post":1,"fauvism":1,"link":1,"art":2,"their":1,"social":1,"context":1,"industrialisation":1,"modern":1,"city":1,"life":1,"new":1,"paint":1,"tubes":1,"enabling":1,"outdoor":1,"painting":1,"mathematics":1,"geometry":1,"parallel":1,"lines":1,"angles":1,"ratios":1,"diminishing":1,"size":1,"vanishing":1,"point":3,"limit":1,"constructing":1,"accurate":1,"one":1,"two":1,"grids":1,"uses":1,"same":1,"reasoning":1,"scale":1,"proportion":1,"maths":1,"language":1,"literature":1,"critique":1,"writing":1,"using":1,"precise":1,"vocabulary":1,"describing":1,"then":2,"analysing":1,"evaluating":1,"artwork":1,"structuring":1,"paragraph":1,"evidence":1,"explanation":1,"mirrors":1,"analytical":1,"essay":1,"skills":1,"narrative":1,"connects":1,"storytelling":1,"sequencing":1,"science":1,"extension":1,"colour":2,"light":2,"how":1,"eye":1,"perceives":1,"optical":1,"mixing":1,"why":1,"complementary":1,"colours":1,"intensify":1,"each":1,"other":1,"links":1,"physics":1,"human":1,"vision":1}'::jsonb),
