('chunk_930073a1a3d6d4ef8f','file_c827a0b7bfd97ec469','world-languages.md','2. Shared "Language Acquisition (Emergent)" Unit Framework','*(Applies identically to Spanish, French and Hindi. Each unit is presented once here; language-specific vocabulary, grammar and text samples follow in Sections 3–4.)*

The four **Key Concepts** most used in Language Acquisition are **Communication, Connections, Creativity and Culture**. Each unit below selects a Key Concept, related concepts, a Global Context, a Statement of Inquiry (SOI) and three inquiry questions.

